{"tid":539263,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解咁多人想合法化大麻，而唔係非刑事化？","createTime":"2018-01-24T11:50:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T11:02:19.000Z","uid":98915,"like":25,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"615b8c4c9f6290f5297363e1488b2e8e0753cdc2","tid":539263,"uid":98915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T11:50:31.000Z","msg":"老老豆豆 食嘅人會照食 唔食嘅點都唔會食<br />\n而且又有政府管制 唔可以係公眾地方食 <br />\n打擊黑市之餘 仲限埋啲未成年人士接觸毒品<br />\n俾啲人排解壓力 起碼香港都會少啲自殺 <br />\n政府又可以有多一筆收入<br />\n依家咁多研究講有冇害都五十五十 唔知最後點啦<br />\n但咁樣俾大家責任自負的話 我又覺得行得通喎<br />\n至少我覺得真係比煙好 唔會累人累物成街死<br />\n我覺得全面禁煙 非刑事化大麻係利多於弊<br />\n<br />\n巴打們點睇？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：冇食"},{"pid":"7174d6ed2d9d52856cfaa0b3187347a785642bf5","tid":539263,"uid":144466,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T11:53:40.000Z","msg":"認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32aa17521ce4e7d0f927a714e6db65046a194ef4","tid":539263,"uid":42636,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T11:55:32.000Z","msg":"實有人支持，d 女比人輪完都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08cddbf670d9ece60fdc6ed08301f0042e0fcdc5","tid":539263,"uid":20227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T11:56:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d8a4a1a623334efe9972ee1c852414b8dd662330","tid":539263,"uid":144466,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T11:57:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>實有人支持，d 女比人輪完都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁係應該禁酒wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c63aedf9e835d5783ce088a041f9bd7c15e8d4c","tid":539263,"uid":162409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T11:59:01.000Z","msg":"試過返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19775e202cdd6125656bdcccc912d124dc876d15","tid":539263,"uid":98915,"like":0,"disl